articles.title: BAFTA Awards Producers Tease Show Surprises and Whether Barry Keoghan Will Cameo During Sophie Ellis-Bextor’s Set - Variety
articles.description: This year's BAFTA Awards producers break down what audiences can expect on Sunday night.
articles.content: Last year’s BAFTA ceremony was a star-studded affair, with Richard E. Grant on hosting duties, an (unintentionally) viral rap from Ariana DeBose and the Prince and Princess of Wales in the audience.… [+6470 chars]
